#  Rem:  This is a driver for the Acromag IP231 16-channel 
#        Industry Pack (IP) analog output card. 
#
#  Auth: 29-Aug-2007, Sheng Peng         (PENGS)
#  Rev:  dd-mmm-yyyy, Reviewer's Name    (USERNAME)
#--------------------------------------------------------------
#  Mod:
#        dd-mmm-yyyy, First Lastname     (USERNAME):
#          comment
